1
00:00:00,440 --> 00:00:02,110
(All characters, locations,
organizations, and incidents...)

2
00:00:02,110 --> 00:00:03,840
(in this drama are fictional.)

3
00:00:03,840 --> 00:00:05,180
(This production followed
all guidelines for young actors.)

4
00:00:06,540 --> 00:00:09,280
You're going to say yourself
that the video was fake?

5
00:00:09,610 --> 00:00:10,620
That's right.

6
00:00:11,250 --> 00:00:14,190
It's the only way it can look like
I'm saving Jin Tae Seok.

7
00:00:14,420 --> 00:00:16,190
Jung Won,
you don't have to go that far.

8
00:00:16,190 --> 00:00:17,290
You're only human.

9
00:00:18,160 --> 00:00:19,960
Your own father
tried to have you killed.

10
00:00:20,890 --> 00:00:22,360
The whole world needs to know.

11
00:00:23,030 --> 00:00:25,260
I absolutely will not allow it.

12
00:00:25,260 --> 00:00:26,260
I'm against it too.

13
00:00:28,070 --> 00:00:30,900
This is my choice and decision.

14
00:00:31,940 --> 00:00:32,940
Please, trust me,

15
00:00:33,510 --> 00:00:35,610
Mom and Ha Neul.

16
00:00:57,160 --> 00:00:59,900
You can do this, Cha Jung Won.

17
00:01:06,300 --> 00:01:07,310
(Kunhyang Group)

18
00:01:07,310 --> 00:01:08,440
(Episode 98)

19
00:01:11,480 --> 00:01:12,980
Regarding the video
circulating online...

20
00:01:13,340 --> 00:01:16,210
involving Honorary Chairman Jin Tae Seok
and me,

21
00:01:16,820 --> 00:01:19,080
I am here today to state my position
as the party involved.

22
00:01:22,020 --> 00:01:25,490
The video shows
numerous signs of editing...

23
00:01:25,660 --> 00:01:27,860
and digital alteration.

24
00:01:28,830 --> 00:01:30,460
It's a highly sophisticated fabrication,

25
00:01:30,460 --> 00:01:32,060
believed to be a deepfake.

26
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:37,600
Someone stole footage and audio...

27
00:01:37,600 --> 00:01:39,500
of the Honorary Chairman and me...

28
00:01:39,900 --> 00:01:42,270
and manipulated it
to look like a real incident.

29
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:45,440
A formal analysis
by a professional agency...

30
00:01:45,880 --> 00:01:47,110
is also currently underway.

31
00:01:47,350 --> 00:01:50,320
So are you saying
that nothing in the video happened?

32
00:01:53,490 --> 00:01:54,550
That's correct.

33
00:01:54,550 --> 00:01:56,250
At a conference in the past,

34
00:01:56,490 --> 00:01:57,820
Former Vice Chairman Joo Ha Neul
said that...

35
00:01:57,820 --> 00:01:59,860
you had suffered a severe fall.

36
00:02:01,030 --> 00:02:02,590
Is this completely unrelated
to that incident?

37
00:02:03,190 --> 00:02:06,200
I received treatment in the past
for a personal accident.

38
00:02:07,030 --> 00:02:10,940
However, that fact is the very proof
that this video was doctored.

39
00:02:11,270 --> 00:02:12,470
How is that proof?

40
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:14,810
The people behind this...

41
00:02:14,810 --> 00:02:17,380
already had my medical
and accident records.

42
00:02:17,910 --> 00:02:20,140
They exploited
my real-life trauma...

43
00:02:20,510 --> 00:02:22,850
to frame the Honorary Chairman
as the assailant.

44
00:02:23,920 --> 00:02:25,680
This is blatant
defamation of character...

45
00:02:26,320 --> 00:02:28,820
and a serious crime
that misuses technology.

46
00:02:29,620 --> 00:02:31,220
So you believe there's someone
orchestrating this?

47
00:02:32,560 --> 00:02:34,390
It appears to be an attempt
to tarnish Kunhyang's image...

48
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:36,590
and to put
Honorary Chairman Jin Tae Seok...

49
00:02:36,830 --> 00:02:39,100
on trial
in the court of public opinion.

50
00:02:39,700 --> 00:02:43,470
Our legal team is currently
tracing the source of the leak.

51
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:45,900
We will ensure that the people
who conspired in this...

52
00:02:47,340 --> 00:02:51,080
will be held legally accountable.

53
00:02:55,610 --> 00:02:56,680
(Kunhyang's Chief Director
Jin Jung Won:)

54
00:02:56,680 --> 00:02:57,850
("Circulated Video Proven Fake,
Fraud Using Accident History.")

55
00:02:58,720 --> 00:03:02,350
She's reopening her own wounds
to use as a shield for Jin Tae Seok?

56
00:03:03,020 --> 00:03:04,220
I did not see this coming at all.

57
00:03:04,220 --> 00:03:05,260
(Chairman Gong Nan Sook)

58
00:03:05,260 --> 00:03:06,260
That vicious witch.

59
00:03:06,820 --> 00:03:09,560
To think she'd capitalize
on her own misfortune.

60
00:03:10,400 --> 00:03:12,100
Do you really think she's doing
this for Jin Tae Seok?

61
00:03:12,230 --> 00:03:15,270
She's likely trying to win his trust
to solidify her own position.

62
00:03:15,630 --> 00:03:17,140
No, I think...

63
00:03:17,370 --> 00:03:19,900
she plans on using Ha Neul
as a stepping stone.

64
00:03:20,370 --> 00:03:22,970
My foolish Young Chae
set the stage for her,

65
00:03:22,970 --> 00:03:24,910
and now Cha Jung Won,

66
00:03:24,980 --> 00:03:27,810
I mean, that crafty Jin Jung Won
is pulling all the strings.

67
00:03:33,380 --> 00:03:34,590
(Kunhyang's Chief Director
Jin Jung Won:)

68
00:03:34,590 --> 00:03:35,590
("Circulated Video Proven Fake,
Fraud Using Accident History.")

69
00:03:42,060 --> 00:03:45,830
That's my daughter, Jin Jung Won.
Surely you can see that, right?

70
00:03:45,930 --> 00:03:48,630
Our Jung Won definitely takes
after you more than me.

71
00:03:49,300 --> 00:03:51,040
I can finally breathe
a sigh of relief.

72
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:55,570
She herself said it was doctored.
Who's going to argue with that?

73
00:03:55,840 --> 00:03:58,210
I never thought Jung Won
would go this far.

74
00:03:59,040 --> 00:04:01,080
What did you promise her?

75
00:04:01,250 --> 00:04:03,720
Promise her what?
I've given her more than enough.

76
00:04:06,050 --> 00:04:08,220
It's cute when
you get a little jealous.

77
00:04:09,620 --> 00:04:12,890
How far will you and Jung Won go?

78
00:04:14,090 --> 00:04:16,190
You're turning Jung Won into you.

79
00:04:17,200 --> 00:04:18,400
Is that really
the right thing to do?

80
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:23,370
Lately, I find myself wishing
I'd met Jung Won sooner.

81
00:04:25,840 --> 00:04:29,540
I know. If only it were sooner,

82
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:32,140
Jin Tae Seok,

83
00:04:32,580 --> 00:04:35,450
you could have been destroyed
much sooner.

84
00:04:38,780 --> 00:04:41,350
Excellent work. Just excellent.

85
00:04:42,150 --> 00:04:43,190
You've been through a lot.

86
00:04:45,220 --> 00:04:47,530
I need a moment alone with Jung Won.

87
00:05:06,580 --> 00:05:09,610
Does this contain the slush fund
transaction records you manage?

88
00:05:09,950 --> 00:05:11,450
I kept my word.

89
00:05:12,380 --> 00:05:14,590
This isn't all of it, is it?

90
00:05:14,650 --> 00:05:17,960
You think I'd hand over
my entire lifeline all at once?

91
00:05:17,990 --> 00:05:21,690
If you truly trusted me,
you'd entrust me with everything.

92
00:05:22,160 --> 00:05:23,590
Maybe someday.

93
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:25,330
How about lunch?

94
00:05:26,500 --> 00:05:29,100
Some other time. I have other plans.

95
00:05:42,550 --> 00:05:44,080
You're just as feisty as they said.

96
00:05:45,020 --> 00:05:46,420
You wanted to see me?

97
00:05:49,690 --> 00:05:52,790
I think you're the one
who wanted to see me first.

98
00:05:53,260 --> 00:05:54,260
Am I wrong?

99
00:05:56,490 --> 00:06:00,100
You're right.
You're very good at reading people.

100
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:02,300
You've been in a tough spot lately.

101
00:06:02,830 --> 00:06:04,240
Since your money has been cut off.

102
00:06:05,240 --> 00:06:06,500
Well...

103
00:06:07,410 --> 00:06:10,410
Unlike Advisor Han Hye Ra,
you prefer to be direct.

104
00:06:10,580 --> 00:06:13,540
Beating around the bush
isn't really my style.

105
00:06:28,060 --> 00:06:30,330
Let's get straight to business.

106
00:06:30,390 --> 00:06:31,760
I can reestablish...

107
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:33,130
your blocked cash flow.

108
00:06:35,070 --> 00:06:36,770
You're still young.

109
00:06:37,030 --> 00:06:38,970
That bravado could cause trouble.

110
00:06:39,070 --> 00:06:41,240
We're not talking
about a couple of bucks.

111
00:06:41,670 --> 00:06:43,240
Our allowance amounts
to five million dollars a year.

112
00:06:46,340 --> 00:06:48,150
I'll wire you one million dollars
to start...

113
00:06:48,710 --> 00:06:49,710
as a little taste.

114
00:06:59,860 --> 00:07:02,830
The total amount I can offer you
is three million.

115
00:07:04,400 --> 00:07:06,300
So you're short of two million?

116
00:07:06,300 --> 00:07:08,000
Not necessarily.

117
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:11,840
I'm the one
who has the Swiss account.

118
00:07:13,770 --> 00:07:16,710
You stole it from Jin Tae Seok?
A daughter stealing from her father?

119
00:07:16,770 --> 00:07:18,640
You don't actually believe...

120
00:07:19,010 --> 00:07:22,450
the announcement that
the rooftop video was faked, right?

121
00:07:23,350 --> 00:07:28,020
You lied to take down Jin Tae Seok?
Darn it.

122
00:07:29,320 --> 00:07:30,860
If I call Jin Tae Seok right now...

123
00:07:30,860 --> 00:07:32,490
to tell him to get
his daughter in line...

124
00:07:32,560 --> 00:07:33,560
Five million dollars.

125
00:07:33,930 --> 00:07:36,360
No, three million's off the table.

126
00:07:36,360 --> 00:07:37,900
Why only three million?

127
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:41,100
Those are pretty stingy terms
for starting a new partnership.

128
00:07:41,200 --> 00:07:43,000
I'm not going to hand it all over
with no strings attached.

129
00:07:43,470 --> 00:07:45,400
To see if you even deserve
that five-million allowance,

130
00:07:45,840 --> 00:07:48,240
- I need to test the waters first.
- And after that?

131
00:07:48,310 --> 00:07:51,710
If I think we're a good fit,
then who knows?

132
00:07:52,110 --> 00:07:54,910
That five million could become six,
or even seven million.

133
00:07:55,350 --> 00:07:56,480
And if I refuse?

134
00:07:56,650 --> 00:07:59,220
Then the old man
will miss his window to cut ties...

135
00:07:59,550 --> 00:08:00,650
with Jin Tae Seok.

136
00:08:04,590 --> 00:08:05,960
It's a tempting offer,

137
00:08:06,690 --> 00:08:08,530
but not tempting enough.

138
00:08:08,530 --> 00:08:10,330
Then I guess you'll have to die.

139
00:08:11,600 --> 00:08:14,930
- You and the old man behind you.
- What?

140
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:17,840
I have the slush fund
transaction records.

141
00:08:18,970 --> 00:08:21,470
And the most valuable client
is listed as the old man.

142
00:08:22,040 --> 00:08:23,040
Should I make it public?

143
00:08:29,050 --> 00:08:31,420
You suddenly have my full attention,

144
00:08:31,750 --> 00:08:33,320
Chief Director Jin Jung Won.

145
00:08:33,480 --> 00:08:35,950
Call me Cha Jung Won.

146
00:08:54,570 --> 00:08:55,970
What's wrong?

147
00:08:56,610 --> 00:08:58,240
Se Mi, what am I going to do?

148
00:08:59,240 --> 00:09:01,050
I'm pregnant,

149
00:09:01,310 --> 00:09:03,410
but Se Hoon suddenly vanished.

150
00:09:03,450 --> 00:09:05,080
Se Hoon did?

151
00:09:06,950 --> 00:09:08,750
Explain what happened.

152
00:09:09,920 --> 00:09:12,660
You think Chairman Gong has Se Hoon
locked up somewhere?

153
00:09:14,490 --> 00:09:17,400
Se Mi, please,
you have to save my Se Hoon.

154
00:09:17,560 --> 00:09:20,000
What? How am I supposed
to go against Chairman Gong?

155
00:09:20,200 --> 00:09:21,600
Even you couldn't stop her,
Young Chae.

156
00:09:21,630 --> 00:09:25,470
I think your dad and Madam Gong
have joined forces again.

157
00:09:26,800 --> 00:09:28,640
She must have gotten something
from your father...

158
00:09:28,940 --> 00:09:30,340
in exchange for Se Hoon.

159
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:33,110
Se Mi, please.

160
00:09:37,850 --> 00:09:39,480
Chairman Gong Nan Sook has Se Hoon?

161
00:09:40,380 --> 00:09:42,690
And you think your dad's involved?

162
00:09:42,820 --> 00:09:43,890
Yes.

163
00:09:44,220 --> 00:09:47,930
Young Chae is a complete mess.
She begged me to help.

164
00:09:48,930 --> 00:09:51,530
If Jin Tae Seok is really involved,

165
00:09:52,230 --> 00:09:53,630
this won't be easy.

166
00:09:55,130 --> 00:09:58,600
- Se Hoon tried to poison your dad.
- I know,

167
00:09:59,140 --> 00:10:01,210
but we have to find out
where Se Hoon is.

168
00:10:05,910 --> 00:10:09,350
I've taken care of Jin Se Hoon,
just as you wanted.

169
00:10:09,410 --> 00:10:10,920
I told you to just get rid of him.

170
00:10:11,850 --> 00:10:12,850
Look, Jin Tae Seok.

171
00:10:13,180 --> 00:10:14,490
You can't say that.

172
00:10:14,490 --> 00:10:17,020
He wasn't your biological son,
but you once adored him like a son.

173
00:10:17,090 --> 00:10:19,660
You were grooming him
as your successor, weren't you?

174
00:10:21,230 --> 00:10:23,660
So he was just a dog to you.

175
00:10:23,930 --> 00:10:25,300
You know the game.

176
00:10:25,700 --> 00:10:29,630
You've no right to get sentimental.
He tried to kill me.

177
00:10:29,700 --> 00:10:30,700
That little punk...

178
00:10:30,770 --> 00:10:34,370
I didn't even give birth to Ha Neul,
but I'd do anything for him.

179
00:10:34,440 --> 00:10:37,410
I guess you're more cold-blooded
than I am.

180
00:10:37,480 --> 00:10:40,140
I mean,
you tried to kill Cha Jung Won,

181
00:10:40,140 --> 00:10:41,980
knowing she was your own daughter.

182
00:10:42,050 --> 00:10:44,720
What's the big deal
about blood ties anyway?

183
00:10:44,780 --> 00:10:49,190
Then why are you parading her around
as Jin Jung Won?

184
00:10:49,250 --> 00:10:50,290
And as your successor?

185
00:10:50,290 --> 00:10:53,860
Give me a break.
That's just ridiculous.

186
00:10:54,660 --> 00:10:56,290
I don't have any other cards
to play.

187
00:10:56,560 --> 00:10:58,000
Se Mi is too weak.

188
00:10:59,000 --> 00:11:03,200
So Cha Jung Won is just another pawn
in your game.

189
00:11:03,470 --> 00:11:04,640
Spare me the lecture.

190
00:11:05,440 --> 00:11:08,270
Do you really not know
who has the slush fund account?

191
00:11:08,510 --> 00:11:11,140
I told you to ask Han Hye Ra.

192
00:11:11,140 --> 00:11:12,340
Wait.

193
00:11:12,510 --> 00:11:15,080
Now that Cha Jung Won
is the chosen successor,

194
00:11:15,150 --> 00:11:18,350
she might be the one
diligently managing your slush fund.

195
00:11:21,750 --> 00:11:22,750
Oh my.

196
00:11:24,820 --> 00:11:28,590
What are you two scheming about,
huddled together like this?

197
00:11:28,760 --> 00:11:30,160
What is this now?

198
00:11:30,290 --> 00:11:33,360
Do you two really need to take turns
barging in here?

199
00:11:33,430 --> 00:11:36,370
Handle your fight yourselves,
all right?

200
00:11:36,570 --> 00:11:38,300
I knew it, but seeing you two...

201
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:42,610
whisper with my own eyes
makes my blood boil.

202
00:11:42,840 --> 00:11:43,840
Are you...

203
00:11:44,310 --> 00:11:45,910
having an affair behind my back?

204
00:11:47,110 --> 00:11:50,210
Are you crazy?
I have standards, you know!

205
00:11:50,280 --> 00:11:51,820
What do you take me for?

206
00:11:52,850 --> 00:11:53,880
And you think
I don't have standards?

207
00:11:55,190 --> 00:11:56,790
Don't you know my type?

208
00:11:57,150 --> 00:11:59,860
Me, dating a low-life loan shark
like her?

209
00:12:00,760 --> 00:12:03,190
Hye Ra, you're the only one for me.

210
00:12:03,290 --> 00:12:06,930
Then why does she know more
about our family affairs than I do?

211
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:08,000
And she's even cleaning up
your messes?

212
00:12:08,070 --> 00:12:11,540
Me? What would I know?
I don't know anything at all.

213
00:12:12,440 --> 00:12:15,540
If this is about Se Hoon,
I did it all to ease your mind...

214
00:12:15,610 --> 00:12:18,280
Where is Se Hoon right now?

215
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:20,880
This is driving me insane.

216
00:12:21,150 --> 00:12:23,710
I don't know. Gong Nan Sook does.

217
00:12:25,120 --> 00:12:26,180
Hye Ra.

218
00:12:27,350 --> 00:12:29,920
Hey. What is going on right now?

219
00:12:30,290 --> 00:12:32,790
A wife hunting
her cheating husband...

220
00:12:33,320 --> 00:12:35,990
- for a good slap...
- Hey, shut your trap.

221
00:12:37,160 --> 00:12:39,400
Hurry and escort her out of here.

222
00:12:39,660 --> 00:12:41,430
- Me?
- Yes, you.

223
00:12:41,630 --> 00:12:43,200
- I'd rather not.
- Both of you, shut up!

224
00:12:43,270 --> 00:12:45,440
- Goodness.
- Jin Tae Seok, start talking.

225
00:12:45,800 --> 00:12:47,570
What game are you playing?

226
00:12:47,970 --> 00:12:49,910
- We'll talk later.
- Jin Tae Seok!

227
00:12:53,680 --> 00:12:56,550
You told Chief Kim
you had the Swiss account?

228
00:12:58,180 --> 00:12:59,650
I've already sent him
one million dollars.

229
00:13:00,750 --> 00:13:02,590
A sign of good faith, I guess.

230
00:13:03,050 --> 00:13:05,990
He'll take the bait.
He needs a new partner.

231
00:13:06,960 --> 00:13:09,190
That must have been hard for you.
You did well.

232
00:13:10,860 --> 00:13:12,060
I knew what I was getting into.

233
00:13:12,660 --> 00:13:15,570
To cut off the source
of Jin Tae Seok's power,

234
00:13:16,100 --> 00:13:17,540
I'm the one who has to do it.

235
00:13:19,100 --> 00:13:20,840
I'll do more to help you.

236
00:13:22,870 --> 00:13:24,410
How much longer...

237
00:13:25,110 --> 00:13:27,480
do I have to pretend
to be your enemy?

238
00:13:29,350 --> 00:13:30,580
Not much longer.

239
00:13:31,080 --> 00:13:32,080
We're almost there.

240
00:13:37,660 --> 00:13:39,020
This is unbearable.

241
00:13:39,160 --> 00:13:40,660
What is it? You didn't even knock.

242
00:13:42,090 --> 00:13:43,090
Ha Neul.

243
00:13:44,960 --> 00:13:47,900
- Find Se Hoon for me.
- What happened to Se Hoon?

244
00:13:48,000 --> 00:13:49,470
This is all your fault.

245
00:13:50,100 --> 00:13:53,570
If you hadn't pushed Se Hoon out
and become Jin Tae Seok's lapdog,

246
00:13:53,840 --> 00:13:54,970
none of this would've happened.

247
00:13:55,040 --> 00:13:57,370
How am I supposed to know if you
don't tell me what is going on?

248
00:13:57,440 --> 00:13:59,710
I should've taken you down first,
not Jin Tae Seok.

249
00:14:01,250 --> 00:14:02,710
You said the video was fake?

250
00:14:02,850 --> 00:14:04,680
How could you
be the one to say that?

251
00:14:05,050 --> 00:14:07,650
Right, lying is the one thing
you're good at, right?

252
00:14:07,720 --> 00:14:09,650
Stop it. We're at the office.

253
00:14:09,650 --> 00:14:11,660
Yes, you're the Chairman,

254
00:14:13,160 --> 00:14:15,060
and Cha Jung Won is
the Design Team's Chief Director.

255
00:14:16,990 --> 00:14:19,830
All the while, Madam Gong is hiding
my Se Hoon somewhere.

256
00:14:20,500 --> 00:14:22,200
And I'm just...

257
00:14:23,230 --> 00:14:24,840
a contract worker
for the Design Team.

258
00:14:25,100 --> 00:14:28,540
Madam Gong has Se Hoon?
What are you talking about?

259
00:14:33,940 --> 00:14:36,480
What? You put him in a place
like that?

260
00:14:36,480 --> 00:14:37,750
That's what I'm telling you.

261
00:14:38,250 --> 00:14:40,720
I had no choice but to step in.

262
00:14:40,850 --> 00:14:42,520
If I hadn't, Jin Tae Seok...

263
00:14:42,720 --> 00:14:45,590
was going to take Jin Se Hoon out.

264
00:14:48,290 --> 00:14:50,290
Se Hoon did try to poison him.

265
00:14:52,930 --> 00:14:55,570
But why spill it all so easily?
It's anticlimactic.

266
00:14:56,230 --> 00:15:00,140
I know I'm known to change my mind
12 times a day,

267
00:15:00,240 --> 00:15:03,110
but I might have
a twisted affection for you.

268
00:15:03,110 --> 00:15:04,410
I don't know.

269
00:15:05,940 --> 00:15:08,850
You told Jin Tae Seok
that I had the account, didn't you?

270
00:15:10,450 --> 00:15:11,480
No.

271
00:15:11,480 --> 00:15:14,250
Gong Nan Sook! Look me in the eyes
and say that.

272
00:15:15,290 --> 00:15:18,260
You tried to turn Jin Tae Seok
against me last time.

273
00:15:18,320 --> 00:15:22,060
You said I probably stole it.
Why should I play fair?

274
00:15:22,130 --> 00:15:24,960
- I even went a step further.
- A step further?

275
00:15:25,860 --> 00:15:29,330
I told him you or Cha Jung Won
must have it.

276
00:15:29,330 --> 00:15:30,400
Gong Nan Sook!

277
00:15:30,730 --> 00:15:32,340
Whatever!

278
00:15:32,600 --> 00:15:34,510
All that matters is
that my Ha Neul doesn't get hurt.

279
00:15:35,070 --> 00:15:36,210
Then what about Young Chae?

280
00:15:37,170 --> 00:15:39,010
You don't care what happens
to Young Chae?

281
00:15:39,740 --> 00:15:40,780
Young Chae?

282
00:15:42,250 --> 00:15:45,950
No! I can't let her get hurt.
Young Chae is my daughter.

283
00:15:48,790 --> 00:15:52,760
Hey, where's Gu Yeong Soo?
Yeong Soo!

284
00:15:55,060 --> 00:15:57,630
Where's Se Hoon?

285
00:15:57,930 --> 00:16:00,800
- I don't know.
- You're the one who took him away!

286
00:16:01,130 --> 00:16:02,370
How could you possibly not know?

287
00:16:02,430 --> 00:16:04,370
I'm only following
Chairman Gong's orders.

288
00:16:05,000 --> 00:16:06,740
Please, stop harassing me.

289
00:16:06,800 --> 00:16:08,540
Manager Gu, look me right
in the eyes.

290
00:16:09,110 --> 00:16:10,570
I'm about to snap.

291
00:16:11,110 --> 00:16:12,680
Where is Se Hoon?

292
00:16:12,680 --> 00:16:14,140
I can't say, even if you kill me.

293
00:16:16,550 --> 00:16:18,250
You really want to die?

294
00:16:18,450 --> 00:16:21,320
By your hand, Ms. Young Chae,
I would gladly...

295
00:16:22,490 --> 00:16:24,720
- Please, spare me.
- Talk.

296
00:16:24,790 --> 00:16:28,330
I really don't know where he is.
I only took him to the ambulance.

297
00:16:28,390 --> 00:16:29,390
An ambulance?

298
00:16:29,760 --> 00:16:30,860
Is he in a hospital?

299
00:16:30,930 --> 00:16:32,600
I really don't know.

300
00:16:32,700 --> 00:16:34,400
Then what in the world do you know?

301
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:39,670
The Swiss account. Who has it now?

302
00:16:41,270 --> 00:16:43,770
Tell me. Now!

303
00:16:52,720 --> 00:16:54,850
Let go! Let go of me!

304
00:16:55,720 --> 00:16:57,420
Do you have any idea who I am?
How dare you lock me up?

305
00:17:00,360 --> 00:17:01,690
Jin Tae Seok...

306
00:17:10,900 --> 00:17:12,840
(Damga Charcoal Grill)

307
00:17:13,000 --> 00:17:15,770
How come it's just the three of you?
Where's Jung Won?

308
00:17:15,870 --> 00:17:18,580
Jung Won is busy.
She has an important position now.

309
00:17:18,910 --> 00:17:21,080
Jung Won is very talented.

310
00:17:21,150 --> 00:17:24,280
Though she's not quite as skilled
as our Director Jin, of course.

311
00:17:24,920 --> 00:17:27,220
I admit she's talented.

312
00:17:27,480 --> 00:17:28,690
You don't have to walk
on eggshells around me.

313
00:17:29,620 --> 00:17:31,720
Director Jin is as understanding
as can be.

314
00:17:32,390 --> 00:17:34,560
Anyway, why did she
hold a press conference...

315
00:17:34,560 --> 00:17:37,290
to say the rooftop video was fake?

316
00:17:37,800 --> 00:17:39,000
I know, right?

317
00:17:39,200 --> 00:17:42,070
She definitely told us it was true.

318
00:17:42,130 --> 00:17:43,800
Did Dad really...

319
00:17:44,640 --> 00:17:46,470
I mean,
did Honorary Chairman Jin Tae Seok...

320
00:17:47,000 --> 00:17:49,410
really push Jung Won off the roof?

321
00:17:49,410 --> 00:17:50,710
My goodness.

322
00:17:51,040 --> 00:17:53,810
Looks like you didn't believe it.

323
00:17:54,380 --> 00:17:55,910
It's true.

324
00:18:07,490 --> 00:18:08,560
Han Hye Ra.

325
00:18:09,690 --> 00:18:11,800
Why do you keep
pulling away from me?

326
00:18:17,570 --> 00:18:20,670
Father, I came because
I have something to tell you.

327
00:18:22,140 --> 00:18:23,940
Why did you come here?

328
00:18:23,940 --> 00:18:25,410
I found out who has...

329
00:18:25,810 --> 00:18:27,540
the Swiss account.

330
00:18:29,610 --> 00:18:30,850
If I tell you who it is,

331
00:18:31,480 --> 00:18:34,080
promise me
you'll give Se Hoon back to me.

332
00:18:36,090 --> 00:18:37,120
Fine.

333
00:18:38,020 --> 00:18:39,890
Now that's how you make a deal.

334
00:18:40,720 --> 00:18:42,990
Tell me. Who has it?

335
00:18:45,360 --> 00:18:46,760
It's Han Hye Ra.

336
00:18:47,330 --> 00:18:48,330
What?

337
00:18:49,000 --> 00:18:50,200
You're not lying, are you?

338
00:18:50,300 --> 00:18:53,370
I heard it directly from the person
who helped her switch the password.

339
00:18:54,670 --> 00:18:57,040
Then, do you know the password?

340
00:18:57,040 --> 00:19:00,110
If I knew, why would I be here?

341
00:19:02,110 --> 00:19:03,110
Se Hoon.

342
00:19:03,750 --> 00:19:05,820
- Where is he?
- Find out the password.

343
00:19:06,350 --> 00:19:07,480
Then I'll tell you.

344
00:19:08,690 --> 00:19:09,990
Only Ha Neul would know.

345
00:19:10,490 --> 00:19:12,320
- What? Joo Ha Neul?
- Manager Gu said...

346
00:19:12,320 --> 00:19:13,960
he hacked Ha Neul's computer...

347
00:19:16,490 --> 00:19:18,800
Joo Ha Neul, how dare he...

348
00:19:19,300 --> 00:19:20,600
plot with Hye Ra...

349
00:19:21,230 --> 00:19:22,730
and stab me in the back?

350
00:19:27,440 --> 00:19:31,040
(Chief Kim Ji Hwan)

351
00:19:34,780 --> 00:19:36,780
(Kunhyang Group)

352
00:19:50,960 --> 00:19:52,400
It's been a while.

353
00:19:52,960 --> 00:19:55,070
Though I've heard
your voice plenty lately.

354
00:19:55,170 --> 00:19:57,330
I was starting to think
you'd gotten forgetful,

355
00:19:57,600 --> 00:19:58,940
but I guess that's not the case.

356
00:20:00,600 --> 00:20:02,070
Just give me a few more days...

357
00:20:02,070 --> 00:20:04,170
They say,
"Out with the old, in with the new."

358
00:20:06,210 --> 00:20:09,780
You did a fine job handing over
the chairman role, Jin Tae Seok.

359
00:20:09,850 --> 00:20:12,120
- Kim Ji Hwan.
- Have you forgotten who I am?

360
00:20:13,650 --> 00:20:16,490
Have you forgotten who's backing me?

361
00:20:20,390 --> 00:20:23,930
Let's stop this, Ji Hwan.
You and I go back 30 years.

362
00:20:24,360 --> 00:20:26,800
Fighting like this is beneath us.

363
00:20:28,970 --> 00:20:30,430
You're right about that, Tae Seok.

364
00:20:30,830 --> 00:20:31,940
Between us,

365
00:20:32,500 --> 00:20:34,770
surely you can give me a few days.

366
00:20:35,210 --> 00:20:37,770
And the old man
had better not forget...

367
00:20:37,770 --> 00:20:39,110
who to thank for his position.

368
00:20:39,280 --> 00:20:42,150
Allow me to relay
the old man's message.

369
00:20:43,380 --> 00:20:45,450
"Our communication channel
with Kunhyang Group..."

370
00:20:45,450 --> 00:20:47,580
"has changed, Jin Tae Seok."

371
00:20:49,120 --> 00:20:50,120
Kim Ji Hwan.

372
00:20:53,690 --> 00:20:56,630
He also told you to watch your back.

373
00:21:07,170 --> 00:21:09,070
The point of contact
has been changed?

374
00:21:09,940 --> 00:21:11,010
And should I watch my back?

375
00:21:12,310 --> 00:21:14,780
How dare he cast me aside?

376
00:21:22,850 --> 00:21:25,390
The number you have dialed
is not in service.

377
00:21:25,860 --> 00:21:27,960
- Please check the number...
- What?

378
00:21:29,060 --> 00:21:30,390
He really cut me off?

379
00:21:33,800 --> 00:21:34,870
This is all...

380
00:21:35,730 --> 00:21:37,130
Han Hye Ra's fault.

381
00:21:45,840 --> 00:21:48,410
Han Hye Ra, you stole my account?

382
00:21:48,680 --> 00:21:49,810
I told you I didn't!

383
00:21:49,880 --> 00:21:52,250
- Stop lying!
- Get your filthy hands off me!

384
00:21:52,320 --> 00:21:53,750
What? Filthy?

385
00:21:58,060 --> 00:21:59,920
- Han Hye Ra.
- That's right.

386
00:22:00,520 --> 00:22:02,090
I have your account.

387
00:22:02,690 --> 00:22:05,530
Gong Nan Sook siphoned off half,
so I changed the password.

388
00:22:05,600 --> 00:22:07,200
And Joo Ha Neul was in on it, right?

389
00:22:09,200 --> 00:22:11,540
How dare you two double-cross me?

390
00:22:12,000 --> 00:22:14,940
- I'll make you pay for this!
- Go ahead.

391
00:22:15,640 --> 00:22:19,040
I'll take you down
before you get the chance.

392
00:22:21,550 --> 00:22:22,550
Hye Ra.

393
00:22:23,450 --> 00:22:24,450
Do you really mean that?

394
00:22:26,480 --> 00:22:28,290
You're breaking my heart.

395
00:22:29,290 --> 00:22:31,560
- Don't do this, Please!
- Don't touch me!

396
00:22:33,960 --> 00:22:35,960
Get your hand off me.
Don't come any closer.

397
00:22:47,570 --> 00:22:48,970
Joo Ha Neul, was it you?

398
00:22:49,740 --> 00:22:51,370
How dare you take my money?

399
00:22:56,980 --> 00:22:58,050
Dad.

400
00:22:58,720 --> 00:22:59,720
Se Mi.

401
00:23:00,680 --> 00:23:02,220
Did you want to talk
to me about something?

402
00:23:03,320 --> 00:23:04,620
I heard that Chairman Gong...

403
00:23:05,020 --> 00:23:07,190
had Se Hoon locked up.

404
00:23:07,320 --> 00:23:08,690
Who told you that?

405
00:23:09,290 --> 00:23:10,290
Was it Young Chae?

406
00:23:10,790 --> 00:23:11,830
Is it possible...

407
00:23:12,630 --> 00:23:14,260
you have something to do with it?

408
00:23:14,900 --> 00:23:17,730
Of course not. I would never do
something like that.

409
00:23:20,570 --> 00:23:22,670
Are you worried about Se Hoon?

410
00:23:25,440 --> 00:23:27,140
Even after he tried to poison me?

411
00:23:27,340 --> 00:23:30,050
But he's my brother.
We grew up in the same house.

412
00:23:30,810 --> 00:23:33,850
And now I can't reach him
and have no idea where he is.

413
00:23:35,850 --> 00:23:37,820
If you're really not involved,

414
00:23:38,620 --> 00:23:40,720
find Se Hoon.

415
00:23:43,230 --> 00:23:45,860
I'll try to have a word
with Chairman Gong.

416
00:23:46,660 --> 00:23:47,900
Please, Dad.

417
00:23:54,000 --> 00:23:56,570
To make Hye Ra cough up
the account password...

418
00:24:01,340 --> 00:24:02,810
Is Se Mi my only option?

419
00:24:05,520 --> 00:24:06,580
What's wrong?

420
00:24:07,550 --> 00:24:09,890
My sweet Se Mi.

421
00:24:10,690 --> 00:24:11,990
You love me, don't you?

422
00:24:14,990 --> 00:24:16,990
And I love your mother too.

423
00:24:17,730 --> 00:24:18,730
But...

424
00:24:19,500 --> 00:24:20,860
your mother is making things...

425
00:24:21,460 --> 00:24:23,200
very difficult for me.

426
00:24:24,370 --> 00:24:25,670
What do you think I should do?

427
00:24:26,140 --> 00:24:27,700
What are you talking about?

428
00:24:28,310 --> 00:24:30,110
Isn't it you
who's giving Mom a hard time?

429
00:24:30,540 --> 00:24:34,340
I always respect your mom's opinion
and go along with it.

430
00:24:35,410 --> 00:24:39,180
But this time,
she's made me really angry.

431
00:24:41,650 --> 00:24:43,320
Do you think you could help me out?

432
00:24:44,920 --> 00:24:45,920
How?

433
00:24:46,520 --> 00:24:49,560
You just need to trust me
and do as I say.

434
00:24:51,760 --> 00:24:55,600
My beloved daughter, Se Mi,

435
00:24:56,330 --> 00:24:58,270
I'll need you to endure a hardship
for a little while.

436
00:24:59,340 --> 00:25:03,270
But it's all for me,
your mom, and you.

437
00:25:04,010 --> 00:25:05,540
It's for our family.

438
00:25:18,520 --> 00:25:19,520
Se Mi.

439
00:25:21,420 --> 00:25:22,860
I'm so sorry.

440
00:25:32,340 --> 00:25:34,140
Dad, what happened?

441
00:25:34,400 --> 00:25:35,910
I found out where Se Hoon is.

442
00:25:36,410 --> 00:25:37,410
Really?

443
00:25:38,380 --> 00:25:39,380
Se Mi.

444
00:25:40,880 --> 00:25:42,010
Would you come with me?

445
00:25:44,150 --> 00:25:46,120
You know that Se Hoon and I
had a falling out.

446
00:25:46,750 --> 00:25:49,620
I'm worried that if I go alone,
we'll just end up fighting.

447
00:25:50,050 --> 00:25:51,620
Okay. I'll go with you.

448
00:25:51,820 --> 00:25:54,930
We can't let Chairman Gong find out,
so let's keep this between us.

449
00:26:01,730 --> 00:26:06,470
(Chairman Joo Ha Neul)

450
00:26:10,310 --> 00:26:12,410
(Jin Se Mi: 187-9 Galhyunsaneop-ro,
Tanhyun-myeon, Paju)

451
00:26:15,710 --> 00:26:16,750
The number you have dialed
is not available.

452
00:26:16,750 --> 00:26:17,950
Transferring to voicemail.

453
00:26:18,010 --> 00:26:19,380
- Why isn't she picking up?
- Leave...

454
00:26:24,350 --> 00:26:26,460
(Jin Se Mi: 187-9 Galhyunsaneop-ro,
Tanhyun-myeon, Paju)

455
00:26:40,700 --> 00:26:42,010
I'm on my way to Se Mi now.

456
00:26:42,970 --> 00:26:43,970
Se Mi?

457
00:26:44,210 --> 00:26:46,910
I think something's happened to her.
I'll send you the address.

458
00:26:47,210 --> 00:26:49,210
- I'm on my way, too.
- No, don't move yet.

459
00:26:49,280 --> 00:26:50,550
I'll call you when I get there.

460
00:26:52,580 --> 00:26:55,150
Okay. I'll wait for your call.

461
00:27:12,100 --> 00:27:14,500
Joo Ha Neul, hurry up and get here.

462
00:27:19,540 --> 00:27:21,210
I have a debt to collect.

463
00:28:39,520 --> 00:28:40,520
Se Mi!

464
00:28:42,630 --> 00:28:43,630
Se Mi.

465
00:28:44,590 --> 00:28:45,600
Se Mi.

466
00:29:06,580 --> 00:29:08,820
What is it? Is something wrong?

467
00:29:09,420 --> 00:29:11,890
I think something's happened
to Se Mi.

468
00:29:12,360 --> 00:29:14,660
Ha Neul is on his way to her now.

469
00:29:14,790 --> 00:29:17,290
What? Where is she?

470
00:29:24,970 --> 00:29:25,970
Where are you?

471
00:29:28,670 --> 00:29:29,670
It's me.

472
00:29:30,140 --> 00:29:32,610
Your one and only love,
Jin Tae Seok.

473
00:29:33,580 --> 00:29:35,580
Don't tell me you have Se Mi...

474
00:29:35,650 --> 00:29:38,580
Yes, she's with me.

475
00:29:39,120 --> 00:29:42,650
You didn't do anything to her,
did you?

476
00:29:42,790 --> 00:29:44,190
Why did you have to mess with me?

477
00:29:45,160 --> 00:29:46,590
None of this would've happened...

478
00:29:46,590 --> 00:29:49,460
if you hadn't stolen my account
and driven me to the edge.

479
00:29:50,990 --> 00:29:53,660
Jin Tae Seok, where is Se Mi?

480
00:29:54,800 --> 00:29:57,570
Jin Tae Seok took Se Mi?

481
00:29:59,140 --> 00:30:01,640
See for yourself.
Our daughter is perfectly fine.

482
00:30:02,670 --> 00:30:04,670
Jin Tae Seok!

483
00:30:10,050 --> 00:30:12,320
And one more thing.

484
00:30:13,020 --> 00:30:14,280
I didn't want Se Mi to be lonely,

485
00:30:14,780 --> 00:30:17,020
so I invited the man she loves,
Joo Ha Neul, to join her.

486
00:30:17,450 --> 00:30:19,690
- I'll send them off together.
- Se Mi!

487
00:30:20,790 --> 00:30:22,930
Chairman Joo! Se Mi!

488
00:30:25,200 --> 00:30:28,630
You and Gong Nan Sook betrayed me.
This is just payback, isn't it?

489
00:30:30,970 --> 00:30:31,970
See this?

490
00:30:33,140 --> 00:30:35,240
If you don't spit out the password
to the Swiss account right now,

491
00:30:36,310 --> 00:30:37,940
you'll never see these kids again.

492
00:30:38,270 --> 00:30:39,280
Jin Tae Seok!

493
00:30:39,640 --> 00:30:40,810
I'll give you exactly 30 minutes.

494
00:30:41,710 --> 00:30:43,010
And tell Gong Nan Sook.

495
00:30:44,080 --> 00:30:46,050
Tell her to cough up
all the money she stole.

496
00:30:47,850 --> 00:30:49,390
You two seem to be
on the same wavelength.

497
00:30:53,490 --> 00:30:54,560
Jin Tae Seok!

498
00:30:58,060 --> 00:31:00,500
Mom, we have to find
Se Mi right away.

499
00:31:01,100 --> 00:31:02,100
And Ha Neul, too.

500
00:31:22,950 --> 00:31:23,950
What are we going to do?

501
00:31:32,860 --> 00:31:35,870
(A Graceful Liar)

502
00:31:57,950 --> 00:31:59,390
None of this would've happened...

503
00:31:59,390 --> 00:32:02,190
if you hadn't stolen my account
and driven me to the edge.

504
00:32:02,260 --> 00:32:04,430
Let Se Mi and Chairman Joo go,
right now!

505
00:32:04,590 --> 00:32:06,300
Jin Tae Seok, you bastard!

506
00:32:06,500 --> 00:32:08,970
Gong Nan Sook,
if you show your face,

507
00:32:08,970 --> 00:32:10,270
I'll burn this place to the ground.

508
00:32:10,500 --> 00:32:12,200
Please, can you just tell me
where Se Hoon is?

509
